    "description": "We at Vedanta are looking for an experienced Process Engineer based out of Ludhiana. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Vedanta:\nVedanta is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Vedanta!",
